Alicia Lagano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alicia_Lagano 0 Alicia Lagano (born March 26, 1979) is an American actress. She is perhaps best known for her role as Cristina Castelli on the NBC Saturday morning series All About Us (2001) and Selena on the Lifetime television drama The Client List (2012–13).
